---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";  
export const prerender = false;
---

<Layout>
  <Header />

  <section class="bg-white">
    <div
      class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-4 py-12 md:flex-row md:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-16"
    >
      <div class="md:w-1/3">
        <h1 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-fuchsia-600">
          About Us
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-3xl">
          RMVS Market — a trusted fashion marketplace from Pune, India.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          Operated by RMVS SALES AND MARKETING PRIVATE LIMITED, we are building a
          reliable digital marketplace that combines quality products, transparent
          pricing, and dependable support for women across India.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 md:w-2/3">
        <p>
          RMVS Market is a fast-growing Indian e-commerce platform operated by
          RMVS SALES AND MARKETING PRIVATE LIMITED, committed to providing customers
          with a smooth, trustworthy, and value-driven online shopping experience.
          Headquartered in Pune, Maharashtra, our company focuses on building a
          reliable digital marketplace that combines quality products, transparent
          pricing, and dependable customer service.
        </p>
        <p>
          At RMVS Market, we understand the evolving needs of Indian consumers and
          the importance of convenience in today&apos;s fast-paced lifestyle. Our
          platform is designed to make online shopping simple and accessible,
          allowing customers to browse, select, and purchase products with ease. We
          carefully curate our product listings to ensure quality standards,
          accurate descriptions, and fair pricing, so customers can shop with
          confidence.
        </p>
        <p>
          Customer satisfaction is at the core of everything we do. We emphasize
          secure payment methods, clear order communication, and responsive
          after-sales support. Our dedicated support team is always available to
          assist customers with inquiries related to orders, deliveries, returns,
          or general assistance, ensuring a reliable and transparent shopping
          journey.
        </p>
        <p>
          As a responsible Indian company, RMVS SALES AND MARKETING PRIVATE LIMITED
          follows ethical business practices and complies with applicable
          regulations. We value honesty, accountability, and long-term
          relationships with our customers and partners. Our operations are
          continuously optimized to improve logistics efficiency, service quality,
          and overall customer experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          RMVS Market is not just an online store — it is a growing brand built on
          trust, consistency, and customer-centric values. As we expand our
          offerings and strengthen our infrastructure, our mission remains clear:
          to deliver quality products, dependable service, and a safe online
          shopping environment for customers across India.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

